<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Crossword Puzzle</title>
    <link href="/css/style.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
</head>
<body>
    <h2>Welcome to the Crossword Puzzle!</h2>
    <div id="score-container" class="d-none">
        <p>Score: <span id="score">0</span></p>
    </div>
    <div id="timer-container" class="text-center my-4 d-none">
        <h3>Time: <span id="timer">00:00</span></h3>
    </div>
    <div id="crossword-container" class="d-none">
        <div class="grid" id="grid"></div>
        <div class="clues">
            <h3>Horizontal</h3>
            <ol>
                <li>What irresponsible consumption leads you to feel - DISSATISFACTION</li>
                <li>Giving a second chance and life to inanimate objects - UPCYCLING</li>
                <li>Being aware of your consumption decisions - MINDFUL</li>
                <li>Spread... - AWARENESS</li>
                <li>Journey that conserves nature and supports local communities - ECOTOURISM</li>
                <li>Denomination of clothing brands that care about quality over quantity - SLOW FASHION</li>
                <li>Over and unethical... - MINIMALISM</li>
                <li>Movement focused on ensuring the best conditions for their workers - FAIR TRADE</li>
                <li>This polymer is now in our blood - PLASTIC</li>
            </ol>
            <h3>Vertical</h3>
            <ol>
                <li>What every worker deserves - WAGE</li>
                <li>Just like old times when merchants and vendors depended on each other so waste was not an option - AIR</li>
                <li>Misleading information on how "sustainable" certain brands are - GREENWASHING</li>
                <li>Aftermath of modern living - WASTE</li>
                <li>Simplification of life - ZERO WASTE</li>
                <li>Hyper-awareness of consumption where the goal is to leave no track behind - FOOTPRINT</li>
                <li>Where most clothes end up - LANDFILL</li>
                <li>Support your __ business - LOCAL</li>
            </ol>
        </div>
        <button id="check-button">Check Answers</button>
    </div>
    <div id="start-container" class="text-center my-4">
        <button id="start-button" class="btn btn-success">Start Puzzle</button>
    </div>
    
    <div class="text-center my-4">
        <a href="/index" class="btn btn-secondary">Back to Main Page</a>
    </div>

    <script src="/js/script.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
